     row) and the running detail message; and a `Result` block
     with the relevant fields from `task.result` (build mode,
     skipped reason, triple count, diff added/removed, view table,
     graph name, server-reported duration). Footer logs the
     export timestamp. Box-drawing horizontal rules separate the
     blocks for readability.
   - DOMContentLoaded handler now also wires `#syncBuildLogExport`
     → `exportBuildLog`, alongside the existing hide-button wire.

